### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### API Info
GET http://localhost:5000/api

### Test Database Connection
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test-db

---

### 1. USER REGISTRATION
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "displayName": "Test User"
}

---

### 2. USER LOGIN (use registered user)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

---

### 3. USER LOGIN (Test user)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# Save the accessToken from login response for next requests

---

### 4. GET CURRENT USER PROFILE
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 5. GET USER PROFILE (detailed)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 6. UPDATE USER PROFILE
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Test User"
}

---

### 7. GET USER SETTINGS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/settings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 8. UPDATE USER SETTINGS
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/settings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sprintDurationWeeks": 2,
  "dailyCheckinEnabled": true,
  "dailyCheckinTime": "10:00",
  "aiCoachName": "Sofia"
}

---

### 9. DAILY CHECKIN
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/checkin
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "productive",
  "notes": "Great day working on the backend!"
}

---

### 10. GET USER BADGES
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/badges
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 11. GET USER NOTIFICATIONS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/notifications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 12. GET USER STATS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

